org.apache.freemarker.core.model

Interface TemplateHashModelEx2.KeyValuePairIterator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MapKeyValuePairIterator
    Enclosing interface:
    TemplateHashModelEx2

    public static interface TemplateHashModelEx2.KeyValuePairIterator
    Iterates over the key-value pairs in a hash. This is very similar to an Iterator, but has a fixed item type, can throw TemplateException-s, and has no remove() method.
